  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist Project Manager in the planning of required, allocated labour, materials, plant, transport and equipment.</li><li>Review and monitor site construction activities programme to ensure work completed as scheduled.</li><li>Study drawing, plans, specification and scope of work.</li><li>Monitoring closely of construction work progress, materials, plant and equipment.</li><li>Attend meetings with supplier, sub contractor, main contractor & consultant.</li><li>Attend inspections with supplier, sub contractor, main contractor, consultant & client.</li><li>Ensure quality standard and Safety Requirements are adhered to.</li><li>Ensure safe working practices are carried out in accordance to local regulations.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Excellent interpersonal communication skill, innovative and result oriented</li><li>Ability to work independently in a challenging and demanding environment</li></ul>",
